{"tid":2382074,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《大公報》連日狙擊 暗示為黃之鋒接班人 天水圍社區關注組斥荒謬：看圖作故","createTime":"2021-01-27T04:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T09:21:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":47,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"48aa58dfaf55abe458e9abad065b24c80a4e312f","tid":2382074,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/f-9y9mO79eR8aSjFkpwdUQ70yzM=/802x1294/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HYH4W4UVINDY7N5F3DJ22ITWIA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ff-9y9mO79eR8aSjFkpwdUQ70yzM%3D%2F802x1294%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHYH4W4UVINDY7N5F3DJ22ITWIA.JPG&h=55b09041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天水圍社區關注組創辦人、11歲的王繼祖遭八旬翁施襲後，連日被左報狙擊。官媒喉舌《大公報》昨以頭版等顯著篇幅力數王繼祖與「攬炒派」區議員關係密切、質疑王被利用，甚至就其家庭背景起底。關注組在Facebook發文反擊，斥該報邊公開他人私隱，邊指要「保護學生」，實屬諷刺，又指形容王繼祖是黃之鋒接班人屬「看圖作故事」，強調「主席」只是稱呼，無甚地位。關注組感謝市民關心，重申不收任何捐款，現正準備社區工作報告。<br />\n<br />\n《大公報》 昨以A1頭版，貼出「天水圍社區關注組」創辦人王繼祖與前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒的合照，質疑王是其「接班人」；又稱王曾在其個人Facebook呼籲居民到天水圍區議員林進的辦事處索取口罩，質疑王受到「黃絲區議員林進『關照』」；該報更引述一名自稱是王繼祖78歲祖母的說話，披露王的家庭資料，並質疑王受到別人唆使。今日《大公報》再以A5版面「獨家訪問」施襲者朱伯，並借其所言，質疑王「被人利用」、形容王「小小年紀深懂抹黑伎倆」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/HVZ4DHTPTJHGVIWTPTBBFFYZ4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2FHVZ4DHTPTJHGVIWTPTBBFFYZ4U%2F&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=b7bb38ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2FHVZ4DHTPTJHGVIWTPTBBFFYZ4U%2F&h=7ac321bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/HVZ4DHTPTJHGVIWTPTBBFFYZ4U/</a>"},{"pid":"e5a61b5b554286bef80eaf14ee3ca704cde0abf8","tid":2382074,"uid":240362,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iDznhTUKgYOCjeZ-fCxBT8Cn3JI=/802x1121/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QZHO5AAAPBCOTMAXMSDVXLZ6R4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiDznhTUKgYOCjeZ-fCxBT8Cn3JI%3D%2F802x1121%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQZHO5AAAPBCOTMAXMSDVXLZ6R4.png&h=998a6063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天水圍社區關注組在Facebook發文反擊指對左報報道「我笑到hihi」。關注組稱，報道中有關涉及「『攬炒派區議員』刻意扶植敝組織成員」的說法「荒謬」，指成員旨在幫助低收入人士「減輕購買防疫物資的負擔」，發揮港人「互助互愛精神」，反問「香港出發大聯盟」曾在去年5月向全港市民派發一千萬個口罩，質疑他們是否「帶頭在港九新界進行暴亂搗亂香港？」<br />\n<br />\n此外，關注組也提及王與黃之鋒的合照，指兩人當時在「交流一些社區問題」，並非報道所指的「接班人」，形容有關說法「笑大人個口」。至於報道提及王的家庭「支離破碎」，關注組認為等同將王的私隱公諸於世，形容有關行為「絕對不尊重我們成員的私隱」。關注組批評該報「一邊公開別人的私隱，利用龐大嘅媒體壓力跟全世界揭開別人的瘡疤，一邊滿口仁義話要『保護學生』，是那麼的諷刺」。<br />\n<br />\n關注組強調，有成員家庭不「完美」，但不代表會「學壞」，期望透過進行社區學習、與不同人士相處，從而「培養德育」。關注組又感謝熱心人士捐贈物資，但強調不會收取任何捐款，預告「我哋未來真係準備緊社區工作報告」。"},{"pid":"3a4d3adb822a13fa2f0fe5ad92d561bb685b117f","tid":2382074,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80e0d8ba7193260541af0f71e9d3384d0d7e387","tid":2382074,"uid":36901,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:57:38.000Z","msg":"太公報又煽惑仇恨"},{"pid":"e9da4a65177e32530c7222b93e03fbb6f29538c3","tid":2382074,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a4d3adb822a13fa2f0fe5ad92d561bb685b117f","tid":2382074,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" c